ğŸ¯ Conclusion
State is what makes your React app alive. It enables:
  . Interactivity
  .  Real-time updates
  .  Dynamic behavior based on user inputs

Whether it's a button that counts clicks or a form that captures input â€” React state helps your components stay updated and responsive.
